spec_data.Name: rubygem-warden
spec_data.Description:
Warden is a Rack-based middle-ware, designed to provide a mechanism for
authentication in Ruby web applications. It is a common mechanism that fits
into the Rack Machinery to offer powerful options for authentication.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 05:36:07 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Rack middle-ware that provides authentication for rack applications
